Text:
I just want to state that MP3 is the ORIGINAL format this came in. It was a free download on the venue's website, so I split it into tracks and removed some clipping.

Please enjoy this fabulous performance and don't go bootlegging this shit on e-bay!

Support artists who are kind enough to allow taping & sharing of their live recordings

Peace,

~CC
Great share thanks, just finished Just Kids so loving this XX
